snippet: Despite its size, the $7.5 billion water plan on the November ballot will not solve the problems created by the drought nor is it expected to prevent rationing during future droughts....

headline.print_headline: California Water Bond Won't Be a Drought-Buster
headline.main: California Water Bond Won't Be a Drought-Buster

lead_paragraph: Despite its size, the $7.5 billion water plan on the November ballot will not solve the problems created by the drought nor is it expected to prevent rationing during future droughts.
